Package: growthrates
Title: Estimate Incidence, Proportions and Exponential Growth Rates
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robert",
           family = "Challen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rob.challen@bristol.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5504-7768"))
Description: Simple statistical models and visualisations for calculating the 
  incidence, proportion, exponential growth rate, and reproduction number of 
  infectious disease case timeseries. This toolkit was largely developed during 
  the COVID-19 pandemic.
